:HELP     NAME=dspdeth.
Display Detail - Help
:XH3.Display Detail
:P.
Option to display the object details.
:EHELP.
.*
:HELP     NAME=rnmobjh.
Rename - Help
:XH3.Rename
:P.
Option to rename the selected entry.
:EHELP.
.*
