.*
:HELP     NAME=lpathh.
Path - Help
:XH3.Path
:P.
The Current Working Directory.
:EHELP.
.*
:HELP     NAME=connfh.
Connection Status - Help
:XH3.Connection Status
:P.
The Current Connection Status. This will be checked and updated each
time a request is made. If the connection status is changed to Not
Connected, the directory listings will be deleted and the site panel
updated to show all connections available. If the directory listing
is deleted, pressing F12 will return you to the Site Panel and allow
a re-connection attempt.
:EHELP.
