:EHELP.
.*
:HELP     NAME=atrh.
Attributes - Help
:XH3.Attributes
:P.
The security attribute or mode values of the object selected.
This is split into three groups plus a type flag.
0123456789
drwxrwxrwx
0 = type of object 'd' = directory, 'l' = symbolic link, '-' = file
1-3 = Owner authorities
4-6 = Group authorities
7-9 = User authorities
'r' = read, 'w' = write 'x' = execute '-' no authority.
:EHELP.
.*
:HELP     NAME=linksh.
Links - Help
:XH3.Links
:P.
The number of links to the file.
:EHELP.
.*
:HELP     NAME=ownerh.
Owner - Help
:XH3.Owner
:P.
The owner of the object selected.
:EHELP.
.*
:HELP     NAME=grpidh.
Group Id - Help
:XH3.Group Id
:P.
The Group Id of the owning group.
:EHELP.
.*
:HELP     NAME=sizeh.
Size - Help
:XH3.Size
:P.
The Size of the object rounded to the nearest single decimal place
and expressed in either TB(TerraByte) GB(GigaByte) MB(MegaByte)
kB(KiloByte) or B(Byte).
:EHELP.
.*
:HELP     NAME=cdateh.
Date - Help
:XH3.Date Changed
:P.
The Date the object was last updated.
:EHELP.
